name: Last Night I dreamt of Miniature Cows A5 Full Colour Print
description:
It is digitally printed using a CMYK colours and my own design. 

It is A5 in size.

This design is also available on T-shirts at just £14.00. As well as being available in just black ink as an A6 print at £6.00.

name: Batman and Robin A4 Print
description:
I am a bit of a Batman fan - so naturally wanted to do my impression of Batman.

The print is hand screen printed using blue ink onto a off white cartridge paper. Individually stamped and signed by me.

name: Batman and Robin
description:
I am a little bit of  fan of Batman and Robin - so naturally wanted to create my own impression of what they look like. 

The T-shirt is a Gildan Heavy Weight white T-shirt (Very good quality) with a blue printed Batman and Robin on the middle of the chest. 

Each T-shirt comes with its own ItchyPalm tag that features a T-shirt I, which run it was printed in, when and who printed it. As each T-shirt is unique as they are all hand screen printed. 

Sizes:

Small 34inch chest
Medium 36 - 38 chest
Large 40 inch chest
Ex Large 42 inch chest
